sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Web Interface
    participant API Gateway
    participant Knowledge Graph Service
    participant Calculation Service
    participant Data Retrieval Service
    participant Report Service

    Note over User,Report Service: ESG Knowledge Graph System - Complete Workflow

    User->>Web Interface: Open browser to localhost:8080
    Web Interface->>API Gateway: GET /api/v1/industries
    Note over Web Interface,API Gateway: CQ1: Which Reporting Framework applies to [industry]?<br/>CQ2: What Categories are included in [framework]?
    API Gateway->>Knowledge Graph Service: CQ1 & CQ2 SPARQL queries
    Knowledge Graph Service->>API Gateway: Available industries with framework info
    API Gateway->>Web Interface: Industry list with metadata
    Web Interface->>User: Display industry selection cards

    User->>Web Interface: Select industry (semiconductors/commercial_banks)
    Web Interface->>API Gateway: GET /api/v1/industries/{industry}/companies
    API Gateway->>Data Retrieval Service: Load & filter external ESG dataset
    Data Retrieval Service->>API Gateway: Filtered company list
    API Gateway->>Web Interface: Companies with ESG data availability
    Web Interface->>User: Display company selection

    User->>Web Interface: Select company & explore categories
    Web Interface->>API Gateway: GET /api/v1/industries/{industry}/categories
    Note over Web Interface,API Gateway: CQ2: What Categories are included in [framework]?
    API Gateway->>Knowledge Graph Service: CQ2 SPARQL query for framework-specific categories
    Knowledge Graph Service->>API Gateway: Framework-specific categories (9 for semiconductors, 6 for commercial_banks)
    API Gateway->>Web Interface: Category list with descriptions
    Web Interface->>User: Display ESG category cards

    User->>Web Interface: Select category & view metrics
    Web Interface->>API Gateway: GET /api/v1/industries/{industry}/categories/{category}/metrics
    Note over Web Interface,API Gateway: CQ3: Which Metrics are classified under [category]?
    API Gateway->>Knowledge Graph Service: CQ3 SPARQL query for metrics by category
    Knowledge Graph Service->>API Gateway: Metrics list with calculation methods
    API Gateway->>Web Interface: Metrics with calculation types (direct_measurement vs calculation_model)
    Web Interface->>User: Display metric selection with calculation indicators

    User->>Web Interface: Choose metrics & calculate
    Web Interface->>API Gateway: POST /api/v1/calculate with selected metrics
    Note over Web Interface,API Gateway: CQ4: How is the value of [metric] calculated or directly measured?
    API Gateway->>Knowledge Graph Service: CQ4 SPARQL query for calculation methods

    alt Direct Measurement Method
        Knowledge Graph Service->>API Gateway: Returns "direct_measurement" method
        Note over API Gateway,Knowledge Graph Service: CQ7: What is the original Datasource for [datapoint]?
        API Gateway->>Knowledge Graph Service: CQ7 SPARQL query for datasource mapping
        Knowledge Graph Service->>API Gateway: DatasetVariable to datasource mapping
        API Gateway->>Data Retrieval Service: Access external dataset with mapping
        Data Retrieval Service->>API Gateway: Direct measurement value
    else Calculation Model Method
        Knowledge Graph Service->>API Gateway: Returns "calculation_model" method with model name
        Note over Web Interface,API Gateway: CQ5: What Datapoints are required as inputs for [model]?
        API Gateway->>Knowledge Graph Service: CQ5 SPARQL query for model inputs
        Knowledge Graph Service->>API Gateway: Model equation & required inputs list
        Note over API Gateway,Calculation Service: CQ6: Which Implementation is used to execute [model]?
        API Gateway->>Calculation Service: CQ6 query for model implementation details
        Calculation Service->>API Gateway: Implementation details & performance characteristics
        
        loop For each required input
            Note over API Gateway,Knowledge Graph Service: CQ7: What is the original Datasource for [input datapoint]?
            API Gateway->>Knowledge Graph Service: CQ7 SPARQL query for input datasource mapping
            Knowledge Graph Service->>API Gateway: DatasetVariable to datasource mapping for input
            API Gateway->>Data Retrieval Service: Access external dataset for input value
            Data Retrieval Service->>API Gateway: Input value
        end
        
        API Gateway->>Calculation Service: Execute calculation with model & inputs
        Calculation Service->>API Gateway: Calculated result
    end

    API Gateway->>API Gateway: Store results in calculation memory
    API Gateway->>Web Interface: Calculation results with method transparency
    Web Interface->>User: Display results with calculation traceability

    User->>Web Interface: Generate comprehensive report
    Web Interface->>API Gateway: POST /api/v1/reports/generate
    API Gateway->>Report Service: Create comprehensive ESG report
    Report Service->>Knowledge Graph Service: Gather complete framework context
    Report Service->>Calculation Service: Retrieve all calculated metrics
    Report Service->>Data Retrieval Service: Access supporting data lineage
    Report Service->>API Gateway: Complete ESG report with data sources
    API Gateway->>Web Interface: Final comprehensive report
    Web Interface->>User: Display complete ESG analysis report 